title: Cloud Natural Language - Apache Airflow/Cloud Composer 運算符
abstract:
# Cloud Natural Language - Apache Airflow/Cloud Composer 運算符
您可以使用 Apache Airflow [Cloud Natural Language 運算符](https://airflow.apache.org//docs/apache-airflow-providers-google/stable/operators/cloud/natural_language.html) 在 [Cloud Composer 工作流](https://cloud.google.com/composer/docs/how-to/using/writing-dags?hl=zh-cn) 中添加 Cloud Natural Language 任務
